data.name: grdMiMagamOrder.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE ,A.MIX_GROUP GROUP_SER ,A.JAERYO_CODE JAERYO_CODE ,B.JAERYO_NAME JAERYO_NAME ,A.ORD_SURYANG ORD_SURYANG ,A.DV_TIME DV_TIME ,A.DV DV ,A.NALSU NALSU ,A.ORDER_DANUI ORDER_DANUI ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORD_DANUI', A.ORDER_DANUI) DANUI_NAME ,A.BOGYONG_CODE BOGYONG_CODE ,A.BOGYONG_CODE || ' ' || FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA_SPD_GUBUN',NVL(A.JUSA_SPD_GUBUN,'0')) BOGYONG_NAME ,A.POWDER_YN POWDER_YN ,'(' || NVL(A.DV_1,'0')||'-'||NVL(A.DV_2,'0')||'-'||NVL(A.DV_3,'0')||'-'||NVL(A.DV_4,'0')||'-'||NVL(A.DV_5,'0')||') ' || A.REMARK REMARK ,A.DV_1 DV_1 ,A.DV_2 DV_2 ,A.DV_3 DV_3 ,A.DV_4 DV_4 ,A.DV_5 DV_5 ,A.HUBAL_CHANGE_YN HUBAL_CHANGE_YN ,A.PHARMACY PHARMACY ,A.DRG_PACK_YN DRG_PACK_YN ,A.JUSA JUSA ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA',NVL(A.JUSA,'0')) JUSA_NAME ,A.MIX_GROUP MIX_GROUP FROM OUT0101 D, DRG0120 C, INV0110 B, DRG3010 A WHERE A.ORDER_DATE BETWEEN :f_from_date AND :f_from_date AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.HO_DONG = :f_ho_dong AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' AND A.DRG_BUNHO IS NULL AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003 IS NULL AND A.NALSU > 0 AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.RE_USE_YN,'N') = 'N' AND B.JAERYO_CODE (+)= A.JAERYO_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE (+)= A.BOGYONG_CODE AND D.BUNHO = A.BUNHO ORDER BY 1, 25, 24

data.name: grdMiMagamJUSAOrder.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE ,A.MIX_GROUP MIX_GROUP ,A.JAERYO_CODE JAERYO_CODE ,B.JAERYO_NAME JAERYO_NAME ,A.ORD_SURYANG ORD_SURYANG ,A.DV_TIME DV_TIME ,A.DV DV ,A.NALSU NALSU ,A.ORDER_DANUI ORDER_DANUI ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORD_DANUI', A.ORDER_DANUI) DANUI_NAME ,A.BOGYONG_CODE BOGYONG_CODE ,A.BOGYONG_CODE || ' ' || FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA_SPD_GUBUN',NVL(A.JUSA_SPD_GUBUN,'0')) BOGYONG_NAME ,A.POWDER_YN POWDER_YN ,'(' || NVL(A.DV_1,'0')||'-'||NVL(A.DV_2,'0')||'-'||NVL(A.DV_3,'0')||'-'||NVL(A.DV_4,'0')||'-'||NVL(A.DV_5,'0')||') ' || A.REMARK REMARK ,A.DV_1 DV_1 ,A.DV_2 DV_2 ,A.DV_3 DV_3 ,A.DV_4 DV_4 ,A.DV_5 DV_5 ,A.HUBAL_CHANGE_YN HUBAL_CHANGE_YN ,A.PHARMACY PHARMACY ,A.DRG_PACK_YN DRG_PACK_YN ,A.JUSA JUSA ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA',NVL(A.JUSA,'0')) JUSA_NAME ,A.DC_YN DC_YN ,A.GROUP_SER GROUP_SER ,A.HOPE_DATE HOPE_DATE ,F.ORDER_GUBUN ORDER_GUBUN FROM OCS2003 F, INP1001 E, OUT0101 D, DRG0120 C, INV0110 B, DRG3010 A WHERE A.ORDER_DATE = :f_from_date AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND E.HO_DONG1 = :f_ho_dong AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' AND A.DRG_BUNHO IS NULL AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003 IS NULL AND A.NALSU > 0 AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.RE_USE_YN,'N') = 'N' AND B.JAERYO_CODE (+)= A.JAERYO_CODE AND B.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE (+)= A.BOGYONG_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND D.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND D.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.PKINP1001 = A.FKINP1001 AND F.PKOCS2003 = A.FKOCS2003 -- AND NVL(A.DV_1,0) + NVL(A.DV_2,0) + NVL(A.DV_3,0) + NVL(A.DV_4,0) + NVL(A.DV_5,0) > 0 ORDER BY 1, 2, 24

data.name: grdMagamPaQuery.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT A.JUBSU_DATE JUBSU_DATE ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,A.BUNHO BUNHO ,B.SUNAME SUNAME ,NVL(A.MAGAM_GUBUN, 'ER') MAGAM_GUBUN ,FN_OCS_LOAD_ORDER_GWA(A.FKOCS2003) GWA ,FN_OCS_LOAD_ORDER_DOCTOR(A.FKOCS2003) DOCTOR ,FN_OCS_LOAD_ORDER_DOCTOR_NAME(A.FKOCS2003) DOCTOR_NAME FROM OUT0101 B , DRG3010 A WHERE A.JUBSU_DATE = :f_magam_date AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.MAGAM_GUBUN = 'ER' AND A.CHULGO_BUSEO LIKE NVL(:f_ho_dong, '%') AND A.BUNHO LIKE NVL(:f_bunho, '%') AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003 IS NULL AND NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN,'N') = 'N' AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND NVL(A.NALSU,0) > 0 -- AND 'NRO' NOT LIKE NVL(:f_ho_dong, '%') UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT A.JUBSU_DATE JUBSU_DATE ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,A.BUNHO BUNHO ,B.SUNAME SUNAME ,NVL(A.MAGAM_GUBUN, 'ER') MAGAM_GUBUN ,FN_OCS_LOAD_ORDER_GWA(A.FKOCS2003) GWA ,FN_OCS_LOAD_ORDER_DOCTOR(A.FKOCS2003) DOCTOR ,FN_OCS_LOAD_ORDER_DOCTOR_NAME(A.FKOCS2003) DOCTOR_NAME FROM OUT0101 B , DRG3010 A WHERE A.JUBSU_DATE = :f_magam_date AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO LIKE NVL(:f_bunho, '%') AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' AND A.EMERGENCY = 'Y' AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003 IS NULL AND NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN,'N') = 'N' AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND NVL(A.NALSU,0) > 0 -- AND 'NRO' LIKE NVL(:f_ho_dong, '%') ORDER BY 1, 2 DESC

data.name: grdPaQuery.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT A.BUNHO BUNHO ,B.SUNAME SUNAME ,B.SEX SEX ,FN_BAS_LOAD_AGE(A.ORDER_DATE, B.BIRTH, '') AGE ,A.HO_DONG HO_DONG ,FN_BAS_LOAD_HO_DONG_NAME(A.HO_DONG, A.ORDER_DATE) HO_DONG_NAME ,A.RESIDENT RESIDENT ,FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.RESIDENT, A.ORDER_DATE) DOCTOR_NAME ,DECODE(NVL(A.TOIWON_DRG_YN,'N'),'0','31','1','31',DECODE(NVL(A.EMERGENCY,'N'),'Y','ER',DECODE(NVL(A.APPEND_YN,'N'),'Y','22','12'))) MAGAM_GUBUN ,C.HO_DONG1 FROM INP1001 C, OUT0101 B, DRG3010 A WHERE A.ORDER_DATE = :f_from_date AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND C.HO_DONG1 LIKE :f_ho_dong || '%' AND A.BUNHO LIKE NVL(:f_bunho, '%') AND A.BUNRYU1 = '4' AND A.DRG_BUNHO IS NULL AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003 IS NULL AND A.NALSU > 0 AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.RE_USE_YN,'N') = 'N' AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.PKINP1001 = A.FKINP1001 AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND NVL(C.CANCEL_YN,'N') = 'N' AND C.JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND NVL(C.TOIWON_GOJI_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND EXISTS ( SELECT 'Y' FROM DRG9043 WHERE TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS') BETWEEN TO_CHAR(START_DATE,'YYYYMMDD') || START_TIME AND TO_CHAR(NVL(END_DATE,SYSDATE),'YYYYMMDD') || NVL(END_TIME,'9999') AND CANCEL_DATE IS NULL AND HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code) ORDER BY 5, 7

data.name: grdMagamJUSAOrder.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE ,A.MIX_GROUP MIX_GROUP ,A.JAERYO_CODE JAERYO_CODE ,B.JAERYO_NAME JAERYO_NAME ,A.ORD_SURYANG ORD_SURYANG ,A.DV_TIME DV_TIME ,A.DV DV ,A.NALSU NALSU ,A.ORDER_DANUI ORDER_DANUI ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORD_DANUI', A.ORDER_DANUI) DANUI_NAME ,A.BOGYONG_CODE BOGYONG_CODE ,A.BOGYONG_CODE || ' ' || FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA_SPD_GUBUN',NVL(A.JUSA_SPD_GUBUN,'0')) BOGYONG_NAME ,A.POWDER_YN POWDER_YN ,A.REMARK REMARK ,A.DV_1 DV_1 ,A.DV_2 DV_2 ,A.DV_3 DV_3 ,A.DV_4 DV_4 ,A.DV_5 DV_5 ,A.HUBAL_CHANGE_YN HUBAL_CHANGE_YN ,A.PHARMACY PHARMACY ,A.DRG_PACK_YN DRG_PACK_YN ,E.CODE_NAME JUSA ,D.SUNAME SUNAME ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,A.JUBSU_DATE JUBSU_DATE ,A.BUNHO BUNHO ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA',NVL(A.JUSA,'0')) JUSA_NAME ,A.DC_YN DC_YN ,A.GROUP_SER GROUP_SER ,A.HOPE_DATE HOPE_DATE ,F.ORDER_GUBUN ORDER_GUBUN ,NVL(A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003,A.FKOCS2003) SOURCE_FKOCS2003 ,A.FKOCS2003 FKOCS2003 ,A.BANNAB_YN BANNAB_YN FROM OCS2003 F, OCS0132 E, OUT0101 D, DRG0120 C, INV0110 B, DRG3010 A WHERE A.JUBSU_DATE = :f_jubsu_date AND A.DRG_BUNHO = :f_drg_bunho AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code -- AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' -- AND NVL(A.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' AND B.JAERYO_CODE (+)= A.JAERYO_CODE AND B.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE (+)= A.BOGYONG_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND D.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND D.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.CODE_TYPE (+)= 'JUSA' AND E.CODE (+)= A.JUSA AND F.PKOCS2003 = A.FKOCS2003 ORDER BY 2, 33, 34, 28
